# 191103
Disable Pocket
extensions.pocket.enabled	false

DPI
UI only
use system dpi, not default 96:
layout.css.dpi: 0

Remove full screen warning
full-screen-api.warning.timeout:	0

Enable OpenGL Off-Main-Thread Compositing (OMTC)
check:
about:support -> Graphics: Basic or Compositing
you can force-enable it by going to about:config and enabling layers.acceleration.force-enabled



